1278
00:49:11,983 --> 00:49:13,629
(I raise my head to keep the tears from falling.)

1279
00:49:13,653 --> 00:49:15,423
Take responsibility.

1280
00:49:17,063 --> 00:49:18,262
- Congratulations. - Congratulations.

1281
00:49:18,263 --> 00:49:20,162
Thank you.

1282
00:49:20,163 --> 00:49:21,763
- Congratulations. - My goodness.

1283
00:49:22,793 --> 00:49:24,702
To be honest, I wrote this song...

1284
00:49:24,703 --> 00:49:28,033
even before "WANNA ONE GO" came out...

1285
00:49:28,333 --> 00:49:30,973
as I thought of Wannable.

1286
00:49:31,243 --> 00:49:32,402
(Sung Woon was working on the song...)

1287
00:49:32,403 --> 00:49:34,349
(even before the discussion about fan song came up.)

1288
00:49:34,373 --> 00:49:36,783
(I always think about the fans by myself.)

1289
00:49:36,943 --> 00:49:40,212
Finally, Wannable will be able to hear it.

1290
00:49:40,213 --> 00:49:41,852
I'm so grateful.

1291
00:49:41,853 --> 00:49:45,753
I'll make a beautiful song. I want to do my absolute best.

1292
00:49:46,183 --> 00:49:48,222
- Sung Woon, congratulations. - Congratulations.

1293
00:49:48,223 --> 00:49:49,592
- Congratulations. - Congratulations.

1294
00:49:49,593 --> 00:49:51,222
Thank you so much...

1295
00:49:51,223 --> 00:49:53,532
for working hard for Wanna One and Wannable.

1296
00:49:53,533 --> 00:49:57,432
I wrote the parts as I thought about the members.

1297
00:49:57,433 --> 00:49:58,702
I'll make a beautiful song.

1298
00:49:58,703 --> 00:50:00,103
I'm in your care.

1299
00:50:00,573 --> 00:50:03,053
(The production crew gives Ji Sung a list of the songwriters.)

1300
00:50:04,373 --> 00:50:05,443
What is it?

1301
00:50:05,843 --> 00:50:07,443
What? What is it?

1302
00:50:08,143 --> 00:50:09,412
Why?

1303
00:50:09,413 --> 00:50:10,483
- This is insane. - Why?

1304
00:50:11,083 --> 00:50:12,243
(What is it?)

1305
00:50:12,383 --> 00:50:13,383
All right.

1306
00:50:13,513 --> 00:50:17,582
I'll reveal the songwriters for the blind listening party.

1307
00:50:17,583 --> 00:50:18,853
(Excited)

1308
00:50:19,183 --> 00:50:21,322
You were very curious about...

1309
00:50:21,323 --> 00:50:23,722
the songwriter of song number ten.

1310
00:50:23,723 --> 00:50:26,062
- I'll give you the name. - Is it a member?

1311
00:50:26,063 --> 00:50:27,292
It isn't a senior artist, right?

1312
00:50:27,293 --> 00:50:28,892
What's your guess?

1313
00:50:28,893 --> 00:50:30,632
- My guess is NELL. - NELL?

1314
00:50:30,633 --> 00:50:32,462
I thought it was NELL's work at first.

1315
00:50:32,463 --> 00:50:34,433
I bet it's a senior in the music industry.

1316
00:50:34,673 --> 00:50:39,442
The songwriter of song number ten, which the members guessed to be...

1317
00:50:39,443 --> 00:50:42,173
the work of a senior artist, is...

1318
00:50:42,543 --> 00:50:43,812
Kang Daniel.

1319
00:50:43,813 --> 00:50:45,013
(Kang Daniel, not NELL)

1320
00:50:45,713 --> 00:50:47,182
- Really? - Really?

1321
00:50:47,183 --> 00:50:48,682
- Did Daniel write it? - Really?

1322
00:50:48,683 --> 00:50:49,852
Daniel is good at songwriting.

1323
00:50:49,853 --> 00:50:51,422
- Daniel is good. - Really?

1324
00:50:51,423 --> 00:50:54,292
- No way. - Daniel is good at songwriting.

1325
00:50:54,293 --> 00:50:55,892
(They're surprised that Daniel has submitted a song.)

1326
00:50:55,893 --> 00:50:56,993
Are you serious?

1327
00:50:57,293 --> 00:50:58,322
Did he write it...

1328
00:50:58,323 --> 00:51:00,843
- before entering the military? - Did he work on it in advance?

1329
00:51:01,163 --> 00:51:03,533
(They talked about the next album before filming the show.)

1330
00:51:03,903 --> 00:51:05,902
(When the topic of songwriting came up naturally, )

1331
00:51:05,903 --> 00:51:08,063
(Kang Daniel revealed that he wrote songs diligently.)

1332
00:51:08,603 --> 00:51:10,442
I didn't know that Daniel wrote ballad songs.

1333
00:51:10,443 --> 00:51:12,772
I should've known. Whenever I messaged him,

1334
00:51:12,773 --> 00:51:14,042
he told me that he was working.

1335
00:51:14,043 --> 00:51:17,042
It seemed like he was working most days...

1336
00:51:17,043 --> 00:51:18,412
of the week.

1337
00:51:18,413 --> 00:51:19,442
I had no idea.

1338
00:51:19,443 --> 00:51:20,912
- It was so nice. - I never imagined it.

1339
00:51:20,913 --> 00:51:22,483
Seriously. I loved number ten.

1340
00:51:22,783 --> 00:51:24,652
When did Daniel write it before joining the military?

1341
00:51:24,653 --> 00:51:25,952
I know. When did he write it?

1342
00:51:25,953 --> 00:51:28,252
He must've struggled a lot due to his busy schedule.

1343
00:51:28,253 --> 00:51:30,223
Gosh, he is the best.

1344
00:51:31,393 --> 00:51:34,132
All right. Let's give...

1345
00:51:34,133 --> 00:51:36,732
Lee Dae Hwi, Ha Sung Woon, Kim Jae Hwan, Yoon Ji Sung,

1346
00:51:36,733 --> 00:51:40,403
and Kang Daniel a round of applause.

1347
00:51:40,703 --> 00:51:43,063
(The blind listening party for the fan song ends for real.)

1348
00:51:43,603 --> 00:51:45,542
(A few days later...)

1349
00:51:45,543 --> 00:51:47,042
Where should we begin? There are Chorus One...

1350
00:51:47,043 --> 00:51:48,973
and Pre-Chorus One. It's up to you.

1351
00:51:49,443 --> 00:51:52,182
Just listen to the guide and go with your feel.

1352
00:51:52,183 --> 00:51:53,713
Okay, Master.

1353
00:51:54,183 --> 00:51:56,303
(The member who is on his toes, Seong Wu goes first.)

1354
00:51:56,923 --> 00:52:00,222
(For Wannable, )

1355
00:52:00,223 --> 00:52:05,693
(Wanna One begins to record a fan song.)

1356
00:52:06,563 --> 00:52:09,863
(Fan song recording is coming soon.)
